                            <comment id="194741" author="jhammond" created="Fri, 5 May 2017 21:38:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&amp;gt; so perhaps the short term fix is to change the CWARN to CDEBUG(D_SEC, ...)? Would that be an acceptable fix?&lt;/p&gt;

